{"id": "art-25163", "label": "Art. 25163", "title": "Art. 25163", "slug": "art-25163", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1884902470\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1346\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1884902470\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>63</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1439147776\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1345\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1439147776\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Administratorii\nsau, dup&#259; caz, membrii directoratului <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare face obiectul diviz&#259;rii întocmesc un proiect de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259; care trebuie s&#259; cuprind&#259; cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_293269789\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1344\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_293269789\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)forma juridic&#259; de societate, firma <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul social ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nce face obiectul diviz&#259;rii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1505833104\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1343\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1505833104\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)forma juridic&#259;, firma/denumirea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nsediul/sediile social/sociale propuse pentru <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_942486909\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1342\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_942486909\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;ile</span> de\nrepartizare a titlurilor de valoare care reprezint&#259; capitalul social al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> beneficiare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_321716500\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1341\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_321716500\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)calendarul orientativ propus pentru divizarea\ntransfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1859032157\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1340\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1859032157\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)<span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> de alocare de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social la <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare sau la societatea care\nface obiectul diviz&#259;rii sau la ambele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncriteriile pe care se bazeaz&#259; aceast&#259; alocare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1188446445\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1339\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1188446445\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)rata de schimb a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncuantumul eventualelor <span class=SpellE>pl&#259;&#355;i</span> în numerar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1045097102\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1338\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1045097102\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)drepturile acordate de <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social ce face\nobiectul diviz&#259;rii care confer&#259; drepturi speciale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncelor care <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in</span> alte valori mobiliare în\nafar&#259; de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> sau m&#259;surile propuse\nîn <span class=SpellE>privin&#355;a</span> acestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_908533356\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1337\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_908533356\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)data de la care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social dau <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span>\nacestora dreptul de a participa la beneficii, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ntoate <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> ce afecteaz&#259; acest drept;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_712447035\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1336\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_712447035\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)orice avantaje speciale acordate administratorilor ori\ndirectorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, membrilor consiliului de supraveghere ori\ndirectoratului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_410720160\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1335\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_410720160\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)<span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ul</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social, pentru <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\nîn care <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nexercit&#259; dreptul de retragere din societate, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nadresa de e-mail la care <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> pot transmite\n<span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> de retragere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1565511696\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1334\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1565511696\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k)orice <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> acordate\ncreditorilor, precum <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> reale sau\npersonale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1391108238\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1333\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1391108238\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>l)<span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span>\ndiviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere asupra <span class=SpellE>for&#355;ei</span> de\nmunc&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_126789150\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1332\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_126789150\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>m)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> cu privire la\nprocedurile de stabilire a particip&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a altor <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nde implicare a acestora la <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1557266446\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1331\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1557266446\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n)descrierea precis&#259; a activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\na pasivelor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> descrierea repartiz&#259;rii\nacestora c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare\nsau p&#259;strate de c&#259;tre societatea care face obiectul diviz&#259;rii în\ncazul unei diviz&#259;ri <span class=SpellE>par&#355;iale</span> sau unei\ndiviz&#259;ri prin separare, inclusiv <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nde repartizare a activelor sau a pasivelor care nu sunt alocate în mod explicit\nîn proiectul de divizare transfrontalier&#259;, cum ar fi activele sau pasivele\ncare nu sunt cunoscute la data întocmirii proiectului de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1675695790\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1330\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1675695790\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>o)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nevaluarea activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivelor repartizate\nfiec&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_277512084\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1329\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_277512084\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>p)data <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span>\nfinanciare ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii folosite pentru stabilirea <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span>\ndiviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1164855875\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1328\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1164855875\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>q)data sau datele de la care <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;iile</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii vor fi considerate din punct de vedere contabil ca <span\nclass=SpellE>apar&#355;inând</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_199859261\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1327\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_199859261\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Proiectul de divizare transfrontalier&#259; are, în\nanex&#259;, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare întocmite în\nvederea diviz&#259;rii, aprobate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> auditate\npotrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, ce nu pot fi mai\nvechi de 6 luni înainte de data proiectului de divizare, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> actele constitutive ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> orice modificare a actului\nconstitutiv al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face\nobiectul diviz&#259;rii, în caz de divizare <span class=SpellE>par&#355;ial&#259;</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de divizare prin separare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_975893011\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1326\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_975893011\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;ase</span> s&#259;pt&#259;mâni înainte de data întrunirii\nadun&#259;rii generale convocate s&#259; aprobe divizarea transfrontalier&#259;\na <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, proiectul de divizare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> anexele acestuia se pun la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span>\n<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>, cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\nîn format electronic, prin <span class=SpellE>afi&#351;are</span> pe pagina de\ninternet a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>67</sup> alin. (3), sau\nprin transmitere pe cale electronic&#259;, <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span>\nprimind <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> notificare în conformitate cu art.\n251<sup>67</sup> alin. (1).</span></p>"}